data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Step inside this charming home in desirable Eagle Point located on a quiet cul-de-sac with no shortage of convenience! This residence is remarkably spacious with its large open floor plan featuring 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Entertain with ease in the large kitchen with stainless appliances. Luxury vinyl plank flooring and tile in kitchen and bathrooms. Indulge in the outdoors as the oversized lot features mature trees and native Florida landscape. This backyard is fully fenced. Enjoy barbecues and relaxing evenings on the paver patio accessed by the screened in back porch. Roof replaced 2017. Don't miss this amazing opportunity! Seller is licensed real estate broker.
